{"tid":2193682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電動車電池黑馬誕生？】日新全樹脂電池」，能量密度、安全性都超越鋰電池！","createTime":"2020-09-08T04:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T05:43:48.000Z","uid":22736,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4a339943cb3b943532cd97b016643911b2f1ffe8","tid":2193682,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2020/09/07/japanese-resin-battery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2020%2F09%2F07%2Fjapanese-resin-battery%2F&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqOSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=15f96123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2020/09/07/japanese-resin-battery/</a><br />\n<br />\nAPB 成立於 2018 年，川崎重工的自主式水下載具（AUV）也預定搭載該公司的全樹脂電池。有別於市場主流的鋰電池，全樹脂電池幾乎沒有金屬材質。<br />\n堀江英明提出全樹脂電池的三大優點：<br />\n在受到強烈撞擊或受壓而發生短路時，不會有鋰電池般產生高溫、引發火災的風險，安全性極高。<br />\n製程大約只有鋰電池的一半，設備投資的負擔較輕，量產時也可望大幅降低成本。<br />\n能量密度高，電池容量可望達到鋰電池的 2 倍以上，而且在造型上的自由度高。"},{"pid":"d1f541cfb00aac3979dbad8fd42eebddb22d1d58","tid":2193682,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"10年內量產到先講"},{"pid":"3278c7f1755f7ee06931bcd948709e78d1b97d57","tid":2193682,"uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1f541cfb00aac3979dbad8fd42eebddb22d1d58","tid":2193682,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"10年內量產到先講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:43:19.000Z","msg":"佢地話出年量產喎"},{"pid":"3135697e0d8a1d759986cfa750fefb2c89b7a695","tid":2193682,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3278c7f1755f7ee06931bcd948709e78d1b97d57","tid":2193682,"uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1f541cfb00aac3979dbad8fd42eebddb22d1d58","tid":2193682,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"10年內量產到先講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08